      Since 2006, I've launched Web experiences for a diverse clientele that includes other design and development shops, marketing organizations, nonprofits, and even the occasional large, multinational corporation.

      I'm passionate about the Web, open source, and user experience. I bring enthusiasm, strong work ethic, and broad experience to every project I take on. I do not claim to know everything, but I'm a voracious learner, and I'm always studying some aspect of design or programming in an effort to improve.

