          ## Big Sweater
          ### Independent
          #### 2006 -- Present

          <div class="event-desc">

            I started my freelance practice in 2006. It evolved from producing simple marketing websites to more advanced CMS-based sites using WordPress and other technologies; now, I'm consulting and contracting under the Big Sweater banner.

            Projects have included websites, WordPress themes and plugins, branding, UX design, and consulting.

            _Fun fact!_ "Maglione" means "sweater" in Italian. So now you know where the name came from.
          </div>
