          ## Home Decorators Collection
          ### Web Designer/Developer; Production Consultant
          #### February 2014 -- September 2015

          <div class="event-desc">

            Until September 2015, I worked with the front-end creative team over at [Home Decorators Collection](http://www.homedecorators.com). I designed, built, and deployed new marketing assets (including emails); I designed and implemented new creative workflows for the front-end team to manage the enormous number of assets being added to/removed from the website on any given day; I improved the front-end development process; and I consulted with management re: new hires, best practices, and workflow tools and implementation.
          </div>
